  "api_key": "YOUR-API-KEY",
  "events": [
    {
      "user_id": "user@example.com",
      "device_id": "C8F9E604-F01A-4BD9-95C6-8E5357DF265D",
      "event_type": "Button Clicked",
      "event_properties": {
        "button_name": "Submit",
        "page": "Checkout"
      },
      "user_properties": {
        "plan": "Premium",
        "account_type": "Business"
      },
      "time": 1396381378123
    }
  ]
}
```

**User Property Update Example**:
```json
{
  "api_key": "YOUR-API-KEY",
  "identification": [
    {
      "user_id": "user@example.com",
      "device_id": "C8F9E604-F01A-4BD9-95C6-8E5357DF265D",
      "user_properties": {
        "$set": {
          "plan": "Enterprise",
          "account_status": "Active"
        }
      }
    }
  ]
}
```